name: Untitled Mini Game
description:
Welcome to Untitled Mini Game!

I created this game as a short little side project to test my skills that I have been learning while I'm on the road to get better at programming in general. 

Feel free to let me know about bugs in the comments but for the best way to reach me, use the in game "Report a Bug" button to reach me way easier.

Hope you enjoy!

Yours Truly,

DylanDev
